    "body" : "<pre><code>query.from(timeSheet)\n              .where(timeSheet.date.between(\"today &gt;= fromDate AND today &lt;= toDate\")).fetch();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>try somthing similiar to this.</p>\n"
